reviewText: I bought this thing dirt cheap on a discount rack and it is one of my daughter's favorite DVD's, and it's one that I don't mind watching it myself.  This is right up there with any full priced DVD from Disney or Pixar.
I picked this up on the discount rack at the department store on a whim.  And it has turned out to be the best (any) thing I have bought for my 20 month old son.  He Loves it!!!
